descript.abstract: This data set represents the railroads in Utah and portions of Arizona, Colorado, Idaho, Nevada and New Mexico that appear on the 1:100,000 scale topographical map series from the U. S. Geological Survey (USGS).
descript.purpose: To show the railroads in Utah and portions of Arizona, Colorado, Idaho, Nevada and New Mexico that appear on the 1:100,000 scale topographical map series from the U. S. Geological Survey (USGS).
descript.supplinf: The data set was converted from USGS Digital Line Graph (DLG) files to ARC/INFO format by the AGRC.
